description:

This beautiful & spacious 2800 sq. ft. 2-story home features 2 master suites, 2.5 baths, a third room that is great for office space or a guest bedroom. The 1st floor has an amazing flowing space that has front-seat views of the ocean and mountains, a large covered lanai, a gourmet kitchen with gas stovetop, mini bar, endless granite countertops, spacious pantry, wine refrigerator, and laundry room. Master bedroom suite, walk-in closet, "tea for two" jacuzzi tub in the master suite bathroom. A third room can be used for a private office space or guest bedroom, 1/2 bathroom.

2nd floor is a "loft" style-design; you can have a second office or very spacious living area, walk-in closet, great storage space. The exterior and interior of the home are newly painted, brand new carpet, washer/dryer, solar water heater. No a/c units, very breezy. It is a non-smoking property. Sorry, no pets.
